    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Desks that close by means of a flexible shutter of convex shape and composed of horizontal slats of wood. Distinguished from "tambour desks" which close by means of upright reeded or slatted shutters.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para escritorios que se cierran por medio de una persiana de forma convexa y compuesta de tablillas de madera horizontales. Se diferencia de "escritorio de tambor” el que se cierra por medio de un enjuncado recto o persiana hecha de tablillas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor bureaus die afsluiten met een flexibel, bolvormig deksel dat uit horizontale houen latjes bestaat. Ze verschillen van 'tambourbureaus' die worden afgesloten door een rechtopstaand deksel van riet of latjes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>由凸出伸縮遮板蓋起的書桌，伸縮遮板有橫向木片。和「活動門蓋寫字台」不同之處在於，「活動門蓋寫字台」是以直立的凹版或平板直接蓋住書桌。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
